PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Human Resources and Skills Development of BRIAN JOHNSTON of Toronto, Ontario, as a director of the Board of Directors of Canada Mortgage and Housing Corporation, to hold office during pleasure for a term of four years, in the place of Hugh Heron.
